description:
This is a VERY exciting episode because... Brittany from Season 3 of TLC's "I Love A Mama's Boy" is my first virtual guest on the podcast! Brittany & I share our weekly highlights & lowlights, talk pop culture & current faves, and answer some JUICY questions! You’re not going to want to miss this one!

 

Follow for weekly episodes of the "My Lips Aren't Sealed" podcast, where I discuss dating, fashion, entertainment, travel, pop culture, and more from my life! Thanks for listening!
